import React from 'react' import {Row,Col ,Container, Media} from 'reactstrap' import ContainerImage from '../images/heroAppContainer.jpg' import PortraitImage from '../images/portrairWelcomeImage.jpg' const stlyeImage = { objectFit : 'cover' , width : '100vw' , maxHeight :'93vh', } const WelcomeBody = () => { return (
window.innerWidth ? PortraitImage : ContainerImage} style ={stlyeImage} className="img-fluid"/>
) } export default WelcomeBody
